description: Try our easy to follow Peanut Butter & Jelly Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Peanut Butter & Jelly Cake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 5 ml extra virgin olive oil spray

recipeInstructions.text: Apply frosting to top and side of cake and smooth. Pipe buttercream swirls around top edge of cake, scatter over some nuts and reserved jelly crystals, and pat remaining nuts on side of cake.
